Classes
-------

ColonyAI
    Listens for world events and creates appropriate tasks.

TaskManager
    Distributes tasks to agents.

Task
    Self-contained instructions to achieve a specific goal.

Agent
    Receives instructions from the task assigned to it and executes the instructions on a world entity.



Files
-----

register_colony_ai
    Hooks up the ColonyAI with world events.

task_helper
    Reusable sets of instruction logic used by tasks.
